OL,3,CAssisted dying bill moves one step
OL,4,Ccloser to becoming legal in the Isle
OL,5,Cof Man
OL,7,FA law which would see the introduction
OL,8,Fof an assisted dying service in the
OL,9,FIsle of Man has moved one stepped
OL,10,Fcloser.
OL,12,FPoliticians on the island completed
OL,13,Fthe clauses stage of the debate in the
OL,14,FHouse of Keys on Tuesday, 9 July after
OL,15,Fseven sittings in the House of Keys
OL,16,Facross three months.
OL,18,FCampaigners say if the Bill gains
OL,19,Froyal assent next year, assisted dying
OL,20,Fcould be available to eligible Manx
OL,21,Fresidents from 2027.
