OL,3,CAssisted dying bill moves one step
OL,4,Ccloser to becoming legal in the Isle
OL,5,Cof Man
OL,7,FMeanwhile, a move to make it separate
OL,8,Ffrom the island's public health
OL,9,Fservice, Manx Care, was voted down.
OL,11,FPoliticians also voted against holding
OL,12,Fa referendum into the introduction of
OL,13,Fan assisted dying service.
OL,15,FDr Allinson, who introduced the Bill,
OL,16,Fsaid he is "grateful" further
OL,17,Famendments have been proposed and
OL,18,Faccepted, which he said will
OL,19,F"reinforce safeguards" in the new
OL,20,Flegislation.
